		{ heading: 'A people across the border', bodyHtml: `Nearly <strong>38 million people of Mexican origin</strong> live in the United States &mdash; the largest Hispanic community &mdash; and tens of millions more speak Spanish at home. A Bible that speaks to Mexico speaks to families on both sides of the border.` },
		{ heading: 'A gateway to Latin America', bodyHtml: `From Mexico the Spanish-speaking gospel flows naturally south &mdash; to Central and South America &mdash; making it a strategic launching point for the Father&rsquo;s heart across the hemisphere.` },
