	wordHeading="His Word will not return void"
	wordBodyHtml={`<p>When our Father said, &ldquo;Let there be light,&rdquo; there was light. His Word accomplishes what He sends it to do. Across a nation full of faith, His Word will not return empty &mdash; it will find the left-behind child, the grieving mother, and the searching heart, and it will not fail.</p><p class="mt-4" style="color: var(--color-ink);">&ldquo;My word&hellip; will not return to me empty, but will accomplish that which I purpose.&rdquo; <span style="color: var(--color-muted);">&mdash; Isaiah 55:11</span></p>`}
